headline: Dow Inc.: Q2 Earnings Snapshot
summary: DOW) on Thursday reported a loss of $835 million in its second quarter. On a per-share basis, the Midland, Michigan-based company said it had a loss of $1.18. Losses, adjusted for non-recurring costs, came to 42 cents per share.
